Usage: deleteBusGuide [-help] [-all] [-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}] [-direction {H V}]
                      [-layer {id | id1:id2}]
                      [-netGroup {netGroup | {list_of_net_groups}}]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-all                    # Specifies whether to delete all the bus guide segment
                        # (bool, optional)
-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # Specifies the coordinates of the area (box, optional)
-direction {H V}        # Specifies the direction of bus guide segments
                        # (enum, optional)
-layer {id | id1:id2}   # Specifies layer range (string, optional)
-netGroup {netGroup | {list_of_net_groups}}
                        # Specifies net group name (string, optional)